your channel will show up

00:05:41.790 --> 00:05:43.940
across all of YouTube's
platforms.

00:05:43.940 --> 00:05:46.510
So not just on the desktop
site, but our mobile

00:05:46.510 --> 00:05:50.460
applications, on TV, on third
parties, et cetera.

00:05:50.460 --> 00:05:52.710
So an advantage to putting the
Subscribe button on your site

00:05:52.710 --> 00:05:55.270
is when your fans come and
they click it, now your

00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:57.520
channel will be unlocked
on all the

00:05:57.520 --> 00:05:58.550
platforms YouTube is on.

00:05:58.550 --> 00:06:00.390
Not just on desktop, but
across our mobile

00:06:00.390 --> 00:06:02.300
apps, TV, et cetera.

00:06:02.300 --> 00:06:04.520
IBRAHIM ULUKAYA: Wow, that's
great actually.

